<div id="title">
	<h1>PALINDROMATIC</h1>
</div>

<div id="section">
	<p> Aren't palindromes cool? In case you don't know what a palindrome is, it's a word (or set of words) that is exactly the same when read left-to-right OR right-to-left. The list below contains some palindromes. If you think of another, feel free to add it!</p>

	<%= link_to 'New Palindrome', new_palindrome_path %> <<-Click here to add your palindrome!


	<ul>
		<% @palindromes.each do |p| %>
			<li><%= p.word %></li>
		<% end %>
	</ul>

</div>